## Versioning Scheme\

\f1\b0\fs24 \
Versions follow the format **vX.Y**:\
\
- **X** = major update when new projects are added\
- **Y** = minor update when only the MS Excel file is updated or an existing project is corrected\
(reset to 0 when X increases)\
\
**Note:** When a new release is published, the previous release is removed. Please always use the latest version.\
\
